              <span><font color="#000000"><strong><u>Festivals of Himachal : </u></strong></font></span></h2>
                <p class="MsoNormal"><span>Himachal Pradesh is a very diverse and peaceful state in India. Various fairs and festivals are celebrated in Himachal round the year. There are about 2000 deities which are worshipped in Himachal and different fairs and festivals are held in their honour. In many parts of the Himachal the village Gods are carried on palanquins to village fairs. During these fairs and festivals, the people gather in large groups and dance on the tune of the folk songs of the Himachal.
